node.text: The Rolex GMT-Master is regarded by many as the “ultimate” watch. The dual time-zone sports watch was launched in 1954 and is nowadays more popular than ever. Find a good selection of pre-owned GMT-Masters at our partner Watchbox (Link in bio) #DailyWatch #Watchbox
